  "detailed_description": "Reel and Riddles is a relaxing fishing game where you catch fish by... solving puzzles?!<br><br><i>Guess the moves</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175890/extras/61de1ca11bb56fe0adee24aa47005bd2.avif?t=1731510638\" width=532 height=121 /></span><br>Each puzzle features a sequence of moves from 8 directions. Discover the correct moves within limited attempts.<br><br><i>Learn the colors</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175890/extras/2f5382948c4848329dec127be612152e.avif?t=1731510638\" width=76 height=76 /></span> Correct move in the correct spot<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175890/extras/19d5ed8359824d4b3548f70f9ed59d5e.avif?t=1731510638\" width=76 height=76 /></span> Correct move in the wrong spot<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175890/extras/eaab9b8e718deeb9bccfeee73ffd3bb6.avif?t=1731510638\" width=76 height=76 /></span> Incorrect move<br><br><strong>Game features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Engage in puzzles involving guessing fish movements within limited attempts.<br></li><li> Collect a myriad of fish species, each with a unique twist on the rules.<br></li><li> Enjoy a cozy ambiance, a relaxing world, and a diverse atmosphere. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of fishing.</li></ul>",
